mimes.text/plain: When augmenting data, it is often useful to apply a transformation only with some probability or choose from a set of transformations
Unlike in other data augmentation libraries like
jl you can use wrapper transformations for this functionality
randomly selects a transformation to apply
s say we have an image classification dataset
For most datasets, horizontally flipping the image does not change the label: a flipped image of a cat still shows a cat
s flip every image horizontally half of the time to improve the generalization of the model we might be training
